
Overview of adv awfully

The adv awfully has 3 senses (first 1 from tagged texts)
                                         
1. (5) terribly, awfully, awful, frightfully -- (used as intensifiers; "terribly interesting"; "I'm awful sorry")
2. dreadfully, awfully, horribly -- (of a dreadful kind; "there was a dreadfully bloody accident on the road this morning")
3. terribly, atrociously, awfully, abominably, abysmally, rottenly -- (in a terrible manner; "she sings terribly")
